### 1.1. Useful More Advanced Stuff for Analytical Engineers

- **GROUP BY, HAVING**
  - Conditional aggregation (SUM(CASE WHEN …))

- **Window Functions** (very common)
  - ROW_NUMBER, RANK, DENSE_RANK
  - LAG / LEAD
  - Running totals (SUM() OVER (...))
  - Partitioning vs ordering

